title: Custom typeface or not?
content:
Hello,

Does any body know what this typeface is or what it is based on? I’ve had a look but can’t find an exact match. I’m guessing the angled edges of the h, I, T and L etc are probably customised but i could be wrong.

If you can shed any light on it i’d be very grateful.

Thanks

Hi Richard,

this is a customized [Interstate](http://web.archive.org/web/20090607102030/http:/fontbureau.com/fonts/Interstate/styles).
